---
import { getPermalink } from '~/utils/permalinks';
---

<div
  class="dark text-muted text-sm bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600 dark:from-blue-700 dark:to-indigo-700 text-white hidden md:flex gap-2 overflow-hidden px-4 py-2.5 relative items-center justify-between"
>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
    <span
      class="bg-yellow-400 text-gray-900 font-bold px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded-md animate-pulse"
      >限时优惠</span
    >
    <span class="font-medium">
      🎉 TikTok出海实训营火热招生中！前20名报名享8折优惠，赠送价值5000元的一对一咨询服务
    </span>
  </div>
  <a
    href={getPermalink('/contact')}
    class="bg-white text-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-50 font-semibold px-4 py-1.5 rounded-md text-sm whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 hover:scale-105 shadow-md"
  >
    立即咨询 →
  </a>
</div>
